  "texts": [
    "These qualitative studies can benefit from a large-scale quantitative approach through automated stance and sentiment detection offering a complementary perspective.",
    "Methods and materials DatasetWe chose the data based on accessibility, and to contrast two sources expected to have different stances on immigration.",
    "The corpus consists of articles from 2015 to the beginning of April 2022.",
    "The mainstream news are from the Ekspress Grupp, one of the largest media groups in the Baltics.",
    "Our data covers one dominant online news platform, Delfi, across all of the time period, and a sample from multiple other daily and weekly newspapers and smaller magazines."
  ]
